import React from "react";
import { TextField, Button, Grid, Box } from "@mui/material";

function RegisterForm() {
  return (
    <Box component="form" noValidate autoComplete="off">
      <Grid container spacing={2}>
        <Grid item xs={12}>
          <TextField
            required
            fullWidth
            id="name"
            label="Name"
            name="name"
            autoComplete="name"
          />
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={12}>
          <TextField
            required
            fullWidth
            id="email"
            label="Email Address"
            name="email"
            autoComplete="email"
          />
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={12}>
          <TextField
            required
            fullWidth
            id="password"
            label="Password"
            name="password"
            type="password"
            autoComplete="current-password"
          />
        </Grid>
      </Grid>
      <Button
        type="submit"
        fullWidth
        variant="contained"
        color="primary"
        sx={{ mt: 3, mb: 2 }}
      >
        Sign Up
      </Button>
    </Box>
  );
}

export default RegisterForm;
